---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2025-12-26';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="theme-light bg-surface text-text-primary">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 text-center px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-text-primary mb-6">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-12">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Motus is an open source project. This website is a static site that collects no personal data directly.
            Your privacy matters to us, and we believe in transparency about what happens when you visit our site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Data We Collect</h2>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 border border-line/5">
            <p class="text-mint font-medium mb-2">None directly.</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              This is a static website. We do not collect personal information,
              track user behavior, or store any data about your visit on our servers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 border border-line/5">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-primary mb-2">Google Fonts</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
                We use Google Fonts to serve the JetBrains Mono typeface. When you visit this site,
                your browser connects to Google's servers to download the font files.
              </p>
              <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
                This connection may transmit certain information to Google, including:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>Your IP address</li>
                <li>The page you visited</li>
                <li>Browser and device information</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-4">
                For more information, see the
                <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mint hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">
                  Google Privacy Policy
                </a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            This website does not set cookies directly. However, Google Fonts may set cookies
            when your browser fetches font files from their servers. These are subject to
            Google's privacy practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Open Source Transparency</h2>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 border border-line/5">
            <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Motus is open source software licensed under Apache 2.0. The source code for both
              the Motus CLI and this website is publicly available and auditable.
            </p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              You can verify exactly what data is collected (or not collected) by reviewing the code at
              <a href="https://github.com/motus-os/motus" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mint hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">
                github.com/motus-os/motus
              </a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Since we do not collect personal data, there is no personal data to access, correct, or delete.
            For concerns about data collected by third-party services like Google Fonts,
            please refer to their respective privacy policies and data subject rights processes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
            with an updated revision date. If we begin collecting data or add new third-party services,
            we will update this policy accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or our practices, please open an issue at our
            <a href="https://github.com/motus-os/motus/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-mint hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">
              GitHub repository
            </a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
